description: This file implements utility functions, specifically a factory function for creating a 'Slap Obj Entity' object in the SLAP (Service Logic Aggregation Plane) framework. It mainly defines the SlapCreateObjEntity function, which invokes the creation method for the object.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE SlapCreateObjEntity(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Factory function that creates and returns a new SLAP Object Entity object handle.
